snippet.title: SANGRE SAGRADA MINISTRIES
snippet.description:
If anyone can attest to the GRACE and AWESOME POWER of THE MOST HIGH GOD, I can. And I love bragging on my God.👸🏻

Let those who have 👂🏻 to hear let them hear.
Let those who have 👀 to see let them see.

I am very blunt with my advice, but it's GOOD advice. 

OFTEN IMITATED, NEVER DUPLICATED 💋😌💯


Red Ray and authentic Twin Flame from Queens, NY. Tribe of Ephraim(Joseph). 

GOD AND YASHAYA ARE AT THE CENTER AS TWIN FLAMES COME FROM GOD🙏🏻💯
